    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Fiber obtained from an animal, plant, or mineral source used for conversion into non-woven fabrics (felt, paper) or woven cloth.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
